I"≤<p>New York City must grow.</p>

<p>MNY (Maximum New York) is three things: a civics institution, a game, and a set of ideas. And so it has three corresponding goals: (1) train talent to enter the civic sphere, (2) make it as enjoyable as learning any other worthwhile skill, and (3) deploy that talent in the service of human capacity and well-being by growing New York City.</p>

<p>Sustainable growth far beyond New York City‚Äôs current size is the key to addressing its civic issues and unlocking vast amounts of new wealth and well-being.</p>

<p>America needs visible aspiration; let us revive the great dream of New York City.</p>

