<h2 id="background">Background</h2>

<p>Founder: <a href="https://twitter.com/danielgolliher/">Daniel Golliher</a></p>

<p>MNY‚Äôs roots stretch to early 2019, when Daniel thought, ‚ÄúI‚Äôd like to learn the structure of NYC‚Äôs government.‚Äù That one project quickly became many (and included producing <a href="https://golliher.substack.com/p/understanding-nycs-government">a map of the NYC charter</a>), and his desire to understand the mechanisms of the city merged with his hope for its future. The result in 2021 is a new civic philosophy, and an organization to house it.</p>

